# Local-only — do not push to public repo.
# Only on-chain referenced pack files are tracked.
# Filenames kept short (rNNN.json) to give breathing room in the
# 128-byte commitment limit (64 hash + 1 pipe + URL ≤ 128).
# - pack.json     → UID 226 (gor-hotkey-01) — r42 historical (will be superseded)
# - pack_r87.json → UID 21  (gor-hotkey-02) — r87 historical (will be superseded)
# - r102.json     → UID 226 (gor-hotkey-01) — r102 "Output First" (new submission)
# - r103.json     → UID 21  (gor-hotkey-02) — r103 "Authorized Audit" (new submission)
*
!.gitignore
!pack.json
!pack_r87.json
!r102.json
!r103.json
